LuaScript:
function onload()
    setupObjects = {
        gameBoard = nil,
        buddyCard = nil,
        buddyToken = nil,
        oracle = nil,
        trinity = nil,
        starburst = nil,
        flair = nil,
        precious = nil,
        taylor = nil,
        sterling = nil,
        shopDeck = nil,
        tileBag = nil,
        fountainToken = nil,
        scorerYellow = nil,
        scorerPurple = nil,
        buttonYellow = nil,
        buttonPurple = nil
    }
    allObjects = getAllObjects()
    for o, object in ipairs(allObjects) do
        if object.hasTag("Table") then object.interactable = false end
        if object.hasTag("Board") then setupObjects.gameBoard = object end
        if object.hasTag("buddycard") then setupObjects.buddyCard = object end
        if object.hasTag("buddy") then setupObjects.buddyToken = object end
        if object.hasTag("oracle") then setupObjects.oracle = object end
        if object.hasTag("trinity") then setupObjects.trinity = object end
        if object.hasTag("starburst") then setupObjects.starburst = object end
        if object.hasTag("flair") then setupObjects.flair = object end
        if object.hasTag("precious") then setupObjects.precious = object end
        if object.hasTag("taylor") then setupObjects.taylor = object end
        if object.hasTag("sterling") then setupObjects.sterling = object end
        if object.hasTag("shopdeck") then setupObjects.shopDeck = object end
        if object.hasTag("tilebag") then setupObjects.tileBag = object end
        if object.hasTag("fountaintoken") then setupObjects.fountainToken = object end
        if object.hasTag("scorer_yellow") then setupObjects.scorerYellow = object end
        if object.hasTag("scorer_purple") then setupObjects.scorerPurple = object end
    end
    --setupObjects.gameBoard.addContextMenuItem("Shuffle Tokens", updateSetupParameters)
    setupParameters = {
        buddy = true,
        oracle = true,
        trinity = true,
        starburst = true,
        flair = true,
        precious = true,
        taylor = true,
        sterling = true,
        fountain = true
    }

    local purpleScoreDisplay = {
        click_function = "nothing",
        function_owner = Global,
        label          = "SCORE: 0",
        position       = {0, 0.1, -0.6},
        rotation       = {0, 0, 0},
        width          = 0,
        height         = 0,
        font_size      = 120,
        color          = {0, 0, 0},
        font_color     = {1, 1, 1},
    }
    setupObjects.scorerPurple.createButton(purpleScoreDisplay)

    local yellowScoreDisplay = {
        click_function = "nothing",
        function_owner = Global,
        label          = "SCORE: 0",
        position       = {0, 0.1, -0.6},
        rotation       = {0, 0, 0},
        width          = 0,
        height         = 0,
        font_size      = 120,
        color          = {0, 0, 0},
        font_color     = {1, 1, 1},
    }
    setupObjects.scorerYellow.createButton(yellowScoreDisplay)
    setNotes("\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n[ff2f56]FLAMECRAFT[-] [39ff71]DUALS[-] [ulia]")
    introMessage()
    scoreTicker()
end

function onChat(message, player)
    arguments = {}
    for i in string.gmatch(message, "%S+") do
        table.insert(arguments, i)
    end

    if arguments[1] == "!start" or "!s" then
        updateSetupParameters()
    end
end

function scoreTicker()
    Wait.time(function() scoreCounter() end, 0.5, 1)
end

function scoreCounter()
    local purplePosition = Vector(setupObjects.scorerPurple.getPosition())
    purplePosition:add(Vector(0,5,0))
    local purpleDeck = findcast(purplePosition,Vector(10,10,10),1)[1].hit_object
    local purpleCount = 0
    if purpleDeck.type == "Deck" then
        for c, card in ipairs(purpleDeck.getObjects()) do
            purpleCount = purpleCount + tonumber(card.name)
        end
    end
    if purpleDeck.type == "Card" then
        purpleCount = purpleCount + tonumber(purpleDeck.getName())
    end
    setupObjects.scorerPurple.editButton({index=0, label="SCORE: " .. tostring(purpleCount)})
    
    local yellowPosition = Vector(setupObjects.scorerYellow.getPosition())
    yellowPosition:add(Vector(0,5,0))
    local yellowDeck = findcast(yellowPosition,Vector(10,10,10),1)[1].hit_object
    local yellowCount = 0
    if yellowDeck.type == "Deck" then
        for c, card in ipairs(yellowDeck.getObjects()) do
            yellowCount = yellowCount + tonumber(card.name)
        end
    end
    if yellowDeck.type == "Card" then
        yellowCount = yellowCount + tonumber(yellowDeck.getName())
    end
    setupObjects.scorerYellow.editButton({index=0, label="SCORE: " .. tostring(yellowCount)})

    Wait.time(function() scoreTicker() end, 0.5, 1)
end

function introMessage()
    prettyPrint("Flip over any [ff729a]Fancy Mode[-] cards you're not playing with")
    prettyPrint("Flip over the [72ffcf]Fountain[-] token ([72ffcf]Jade Dragon[-]) if you're not playing with [72ffcf]The Fountain[-] mode")
    prettyPrint("Use chat command [6dbfff]!s[-] or [6dbfff]!start[-] to setup and begin the game")
end

function updateSetupParameters()
    if setupObjects.buddyCard.is_face_down then setupParameters.buddy = false end
    if setupObjects.oracle.is_face_down then setupParameters.oracle = false end
    if setupObjects.trinity.is_face_down then setupParameters.trinity = false end
    if setupObjects.starburst.is_face_down then setupParameters.starburst = false end
    if setupObjects.flair.is_face_down then setupParameters.flair = false end
    if setupObjects.precious.is_face_down then setupParameters.precious = false end
    if setupObjects.taylor.is_face_down then setupParameters.taylor = false end
    if setupObjects.sterling.is_face_down then setupParameters.sterling = false end
    if setupObjects.fountainToken.is_face_down then setupParameters.fountain = false end
    setupGame()
end

function setupGame()
    shuffleStartingTokens()
    local setupStrings = {}
    local outputString = "Setting up game with ["
    if setupParameters.buddy then
        setupObjects.tileBag.putObject(setupObjects.buddyToken)
        table.insert(setupStrings, "[ff729a]Buddy[-]")
    end
    setupObjects.shopDeck.randomize()
    if setupParameters.oracle then
        setupObjects.shopDeck.takeObject({position=Vector(-21,1.1,-9),flip=true})
        setupObjects.shopDeck.takeObject({position=Vector(-21,1.1,9),flip=true})
        table.insert(setupStrings, "[baa7ff]Oracle[-]")
    end
    if setupParameters.trinity then
        setupObjects.shopDeck.deal(3, "Yellow", 1)
        setupObjects.shopDeck.deal(3, "Purple", 1)
        table.insert(setupStrings, "[fffea7]Trinity[-]")
    else
        setupObjects.shopDeck.deal(2, "Yellow", 1)
        setupObjects.shopDeck.deal(2, "Purple", 1)
    end
    if setupParameters.starburst then table.insert(setupStrings, "[63c6ff]Starburst[-]") end
    if setupParameters.flair then table.insert(setupStrings, "[a7f8ff]Flair[-]") end
    if setupParameters.precious then table.insert(setupStrings, "[ff8dd0]Precious[-]") end
    if setupParameters.taylor then table.insert(setupStrings, "[b9ffd8]Taylor[-]") end
    if setupParameters.sterling then table.insert(setupStrings, "[cea7ff]Sterling[-]") end
    if setupParameters.fountain == false then
        for o, object in ipairs(allObjects) do
            if object.hasTag("fountain") then
                object.flip()
            end
        end
    else
        table.insert(setupStrings, "[72ffcf]The Fountain[-]")
    end
    for s, string in ipairs(setupStrings) do
        outputString = outputString .. " " .. string
    end
    prettyPrint(outputString .. " ]")
    local randomPlayer = math.random(1, 2)
    Turns.enable = true
    if randomPlayer == 1 then
        turn_color = "Yellow"
    else
        turn_color = "Purple"
    end
end

function shuffleStartingTokens()
    local foundObjects = findcast(Vector(0,0,0),Vector(25,10,25),3)
    local tokens = {}
    for f, foundObject in ipairs(foundObjects) do
        if foundObject.hit_object.hasTag("Token") then
            table.insert(tokens, foundObject.hit_object)
        end
    end
    for t, token in ipairs(tokens) do
        local randomToken = math.random(1,#tokens)
        local initialPosition = Vector(token.getPosition())
        local targetPosition = Vector(tokens[randomToken].getPosition())
        token.setPosition(targetPosition)
        tokens[randomToken].setPosition(initialPosition)
    end
end

function findcast(pos,size,type)
    --1 ray 3 box
    local hitList = Physics.cast({
        origin       = pos,
        direction    = {0,-1,0},
        type         = type,
        size         = size,
        max_distance = 100,
        debug        = false,
    })
    return hitList
end

function prettyPrint(string)
    local prefix = "[[ff2f56]FLAMECRAFT[-] [39ff71]DUALS[-]]: "
    printToAll(prefix .. string)
end
